Package yt30_lp28.chatapp.impl

Implementation of the common API in the client side, most of the code was from chatapp with necessary modifications.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ILocalCmd2ModelAdapter
    ILocalCmd2ModelAdapter defines more methods than ICmd2ModelAdapter, enables local command to have more access to the local system
    IUser2ModelAdapter
    Adapter for the user talking with model/view, to support auto-connect-back feature
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddReceiverType
    Concrete class implementing IAddReceiverType for transmitting message to add receiver
    ChatRoom
    ChatRoom defines a set of operations of a chat room, implement interface IChatRoom
    CmdNotFoundExceptionType
    CmdNotFoundExceptionType defines an exception because cannot find the required command.
    CompCmd
    CompCmd is a command for processing Component data type
    DuplicateCmdRejectionType
    DuplicateCmdRejectionType defines a failure because of duplicate commands.
    ImageCmd
    ImageCmd is a command for processing ImageIcon data packet
    InstallCmdType
    Implementation of IInstallCmdType for sending packet to install command
    MyComponent
    Message type for sending a component to remote peers, can be used in both user level and chat room level.
    MyImageIcon
    Message type for sending images to remote peers, can be used in both user level and chat room level.
    MyPanel
    MyPanel is a simple panel as a non-scrollable component
    MyString
    Message type for sending String to remote user, can be used in both user and chat room level.
    ProxyUser
    ProxyUser is a wrapper class of IUser, to support toString() and equals() method
    Receiver
    Implementation of IReceiver, with more local methods
    RemoveReceiverType
    Implementation of IRemoveReceiverType for sending packet to remove receiver
    RequestCmdType
    Implementation of IRequestCmdType for sending packet to request command
    StringCmd
    StringCmd is a command for processing String data packet
    User
    Implementation of IUser defining a user in a chat app

Package yt30_lp28.chatapp.impl Description

Implementation of the common API in the client side, most of the code was from chatapp with necessary modifications. Including ChatRoom, User and Receiver, common data types and some customized data types in chat room level communication.
